ShuttleService

Campus Shuttle Schedule: Fall / Winter 2022 - 2023:

  • WINTER 2023 Blue SHUTTLE CALENDAR

Shopping Shuttle:

We will continue to provide our Saturday Shopping. We will provide one (1) shuttle. The shuttle will run during the normal scheduled shopping times of 9:00 am - 3:00 pm.

Pick-ups

  • The pick-up for Fairlane Meadows and Fairlane Woods occurs at 9:00 am. Return by noon.

  • The Union pick-up occurs at noon. Return by 3:00 pm.

Locations

Shopping trips include stops at Kroger, Randazzos, and Patel Brothers. Shopping riders arrive and depart from each store as a group.
